HEADWORD: nonreturnable
<hw>nonreturnable</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>That may not be returned for
a refund; -- of purchased goods, or containers for purchased items;
<as>as, <ex>nonreturnable</ex> bottles</as>. Opposite of
<ant>returnable</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

